ygData.messageBody:
On Wed, Feb 23/00, Sylly Songsynger <jgs@...> wrote:
> From: "Sylly Songsynger" <jgs@...>
>
> Some where there must be some kind of story buried deep in Norrath. Going
> thru some old screen shots, I uncovered this one (two actually.)
>
> There I was in South Qeynos buying up some milk and muffins where what did I
> chance to see but a fight between some guards and some patrons of Fish's
> Ale:

I think there's a couple of non corrupt guards in S Quenos that will
attack Trumpy. I remember in beta, somehow Trumpy and a guard ended up
fighting each other in the water under the docks. For some reason they
couldn't damage each other and they were stuck under there for at least
3 days.
